bruges 0.2.1

Download
bruges-0.2.1.tar.gz

Useful geophysics functions

Status

The bruges module contains several common geophysics functions
used for modelling and post-processing seismic reflection data.

Installation

Install with

pip install bruges

bruges requires NumPy and SciPy.

Contributors

  • Matt Hall
